name: Josh D'Amaro
bio: Official account of Josh D'Amaro, Chairman, Disney Experiences

social_posts.post_text: Had a blast at #SXSW this week. Wanted to give you a peek at the incredible innovation at @waltdisneyimagineering

If you’ve ever visited Disney attractions such as The Haunted Mansion, Enchanted Tiki Room and “it’s a small world” or watched the movies Peter Pan, Lady and the Tramp, or Sleeping Beauty, then you’ve enjoyed the incredible work of Rolly Crump.
 
Rolly sadly passed this week at the age of 93, and we honor him as an animator and an Imagineer.  With his work, Rolly embodied Disney creativity and innovation in the service of storytelling.  His legacy at Disney will live on in the happiness his work continues to deliver to millions of guests every year. 
 
As Walt Disney said; “it takes people to make the dream a reality”. Thank you Rolly, for making the world a happier place.
Congrats to the team at Walt Disney World for the opening of TRON Lightcycle Run! I had a chance to ride it several times and I can't wait to ride it again! I'm sure our guests are loving it!

Congratulations to everyone at Tokyo Disney Resort for their 40th anniversary. It was such an honor to join Kagami-san, Yoshida-san and Bob on stage for today’s ceremony! What a great visit! 

#arigatogozaimasu 
#tokyodisneyland

Happy 25th anniversary Disney's Animal Kingdom! 

There is truly no place in the world like it.  It is not only an incredible place to celebrate Disney stories in a unique way... but also a place to celebrate a message of conservation and stewardship for our planet.  My time as the leader of that park is something I'll cherish forever.  Congratulations to all of our Imagineers and Cast Members who have brought it to life over the years!  Happy Earth Day! 
#earthday #disneysanimalkingdom
This morning we honored Make-A-Wish and all the wish kids past, present and future with a Window On Main Street.

Happy 4th of July! 

I want to thank our SALUTE Cast Members and the US Air Force for helping to make today’s celebration so special with this amazing flyover!

We had a chance to tour the construction site of the new Frozen-themed area at Walt Disney Studios Park. Thanks to all the Cast and Disney Imagineers at @DisneylandParis who are bringing it to life!
 
Nous avons eu la chance de visiter le chantier de la nouvelle zone inspirée de La Reine des Neiges au Parc Walt Disney Studios. Merci à tous les Cast Members et Imagineers à @DisneylandParis qui contribuent à ce projet !

Last week we hosted the Once Upon a Wish Party and Royal Ball at @waltdisneyworld for kids from @makeawishamerica and other wish-granting organizations. We granted nearly 60 #DisneyWishes at once (including our 150,000th) and helping families make lots of memories.

It was so fun giving fans a glimpse into the future of Disney Parks, Experiences and Products today at Destination D23. 

Thanks to the Disney Imagineers, The Muppets and Cast Members who joined me on stage… and to all our guests and fans who visit us around the world. 

#destinationd23

'Tis the season... for selecting new Disney Ambassadors at each of our sites. I'm in Orlando this week, so I dropped in on the ceremony as they announced Serena Arvizu and Shannon Smith-Conrad as the new Disney Ambassador team at the @waltdisneyworld. 

Congratulations to all the new Ambassador teams around the world... and a heartfelt THANK YOU to each of the current Ambassadors for all that you have done to represent our Cast over the past two years! 

#disneyambassador #disneyparks
#magichasaname

Bob and I had a great time visiting Bruce Vaughn and our Imagineers today. We had the chance to spend time with the team and get an update about their new robotic character prototype which made a brief appearance in Star Wars: Galaxy’s Edge last week.

It was a privilege to celebrate our veterans, military service members and their families at today’s @disneyland Veterans Day celebration. Thank you, General David Allvin, Chief of Staff of the @usairforce, for joining the @1mardivband, over 150 Veteran Cast Members and a U.S. Air Force C-17 Globemaster III for today’s ceremony. Thank you to all who serve or have served in the United States Military. 
 
#VeteransDay #HeroesWorkHere #Disneyland

It was so cool to be at Hong Kong Disneyland today to celebrate our very first Frozen-themed land, World of Frozen. The energy and excitement among the Cast and fans gave me chills. Congratulations to all our teams! I can’t wait for everyone to see this incredible new land when it officially opens on Monday. #WorldofFrozen #HKDisneyland #DisneyCastLife ❄️⛄️🧊

On behalf of every Cast Member, Crew Member, Imagineer and employee of Disney Experiences, I want to express my gratitude to Disney Legend Dick Nunis... and my condolences to his family following the sad news of his passing. Dick’s impact on our theme parks business is everlasting. 

Along with our founder, Walt Disney, Dick helped shape our business, create happiness for millions of families around the world... and set a standard that an entire industry must now live up to.

Creative storytelling is the cornerstone of every Disney experience… I’m so excited to see Zootopia open to Guests at Shanghai Disney Resort with so much heart and humor.  Congratulations to all of our Walt Disney Imagineers and Cast Members who have brought this amazing new land to life! #zootopia #shanghaidisneyresort #castmembers
Official account of Josh D'Amaro, Chairman, Disney Experiences
